{"tid":173154,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"一切都係中央","createTime":"2017-03-26T06:07:46.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-26T08:39:48.000Z","uid":91326,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"6f89d5d528d13b829c0a8ff055dd15ff2cb0fb5b","tid":173154,"uid":91326,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-26T06:07:46.000Z","msg":"簡邊個做特首就唔再講啦<br />\n就當真係有位一人一票選出黎既<br />\n<br />\n最後果位特首係咪真係可以唔聽中央既某d命令，去為社會大眾服務？<br />\n定最後上到去知道所有實情之後，都會因為一己私利而服從中央？<br />\n定查實都係身不由己...<br />\n你地睇銅鑼灣書局事件就知有幾荒謬<br />\n<br />\n仲要身為政府官員，自由度係咪真係咁大？<br />\n我知大家都係想踏出第一步，我都認同，所以純粹討論<br />\n<br />\n利申：純討論，唔想有世界大戰"},{"pid":"e81864bcd9e635f19f68aabc15b235742ef4e3cc","tid":173154,"uid":91326,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-26T06:24:18.000Z","msg":"手土"},{"pid":"f886b1c116de007da3d918a69725230cd0515449","tid":173154,"uid":91326,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-26T08:15:13.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4e5cb92984f9d5f48f453db16ce1bb1250f32bf3","tid":173154,"uid":91326,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-26T08:39:48.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}